{
  "openapi": "3.0.3",
  "info": {
    "title": "Ogami ERP API",
    "description": "Comprehensive API for Ogami ERP - Philippine Manufacturing ERP System\n\n## Authentication\n\nThis API uses Laravel Sanctum for session-based authentication. All endpoints (except login) require authentication via session cookie.\n\n## Response Format\n\nAll responses follow a consistent format:\n```json\n{\n  \"data\": { ... },\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"current_page\": 1,\n    \"last_page\": 10,\n    \"per_page\": 25,\n    \"total\": 250\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Error Responses\n\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"error_code\": \"VALIDATION_ERROR\",\n  \"message\": \"Validation failed.\",\n  \"errors\": {\n    \"field_name\": [\"Error message\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Rate Limiting\n\n- Read operations: 120 requests/minute\n- Write operations: 60 requests/minute\n\n## Domains\n\nThe API is organized into 20 domains:\n- HR (Employees, Departments, Positions)\n- Leave (Leave requests, balances)\n- Attendance (Logs, overtime, shifts)\n- Payroll (Payroll runs, computations)\n- Loans (Employee loans)\n- AP (Vendors, invoices, payments)\n- AR (Customers, invoices, payments)\n- Accounting (GL, Journal Entries, Chart of Accounts)\n- Tax (VAT, BIR filings)\n- Budget (Cost centers, budgets)\n- Fixed Assets (Assets, depreciation, disposals)\n- Inventory (Items, stock, requisitions)\n- Procurement (PR, PO, Goods Receipts)\n- Production (Orders, BOM, schedules)\n- QC (Inspections, NCR, CAPA)\n- Maintenance (Equipment, work orders)\n- Mold (Mold tracking, shot counts)\n- Delivery (Shipments, receipts)\n- ISO (Documents, audits, findings)\n- CRM (Tickets, support)",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "contact": {
      "name": "Ogami ERP Team"
    }
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "http://localhost:8000/api/v1",
      "description": "Local development server"
    },
    {
      "url": "https://api.ogami-erp.local/api/v1",
      "description": "Production server"
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/auth/login": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Authentication"],
        "summary": "User login",
        "description": "Authenticate user and create session",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LoginRequest"
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Login successful",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LoginResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "Invalid credentials"
          },
          "422": {
            "description": "Validation error"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/auth/logout": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Authentication"],
        "summary": "User logout",
        "security": [{"sanctum": []}],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Logout successful"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/auth/me": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Authentication"],
        "summary": "Get current user",
        "security": [{"sanctum": []}],
